@startuml
skinparam maxMessageSize 150
skinparam ParticipantPadding 20
skinparam BoxPadding 10
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Multi-Source Data Acquisition Sequence

participant "RainfallGenerator" as RG
participant "RainDataManager" as RDM
participant "SAIHJucarFetcher\n(extends BaseFetcher)" as Fetcher
database "Auxiliary Files\n(CSV / JSON)" as LocalFiles
boundary "SAIH Júcar Portal\n(Web / PDFs)" as SAIHWeb

activate RG
RG -> RDM: fetch_all(bounds, start_date, end_date, target_crs)
activate RDM

note right of RDM
  Facade pattern: Iterates over
  all registered BaseFetchers
end note

RDM -> Fetcher: run(bounds, start_date, end_date, target_crs)
activate Fetcher

== 1. Station Discovery & Spatial Filtering ==

Fetcher -> Fetcher: fetch_stations()
activate Fetcher
Fetcher -> LocalFiles: Read jucar_stations.csv
LocalFiles --> Fetcher: List<StationMetadata>
deactivate Fetcher

loop for each station
    Fetcher -> Fetcher: reproject_station(station, target_crs)
    note right: Coordinate transformation\nto target EPSG
    
    Fetcher -> Fetcher: is_station_relevant(station, bounds)
    note right: Spatial filtering:\nBounding box check
end
note left of Fetcher: Filtered list of\nrelevant_stations

== 2. Data Extraction & Parsing ==

Fetcher -> Fetcher: fetch_data(relevant_stations, start, end)
activate Fetcher

loop for each date in simulation range
    Fetcher -> SAIHWeb: Download daily PDF Reports
    SAIHWeb --> Fetcher: PDF file
    
    Fetcher -> Fetcher: Parse PDF text (pdfplumber)
    
    Fetcher -> LocalFiles: Query station_pdf_mapping.json
    LocalFiles --> Fetcher: Mapped Station IDs
    
    Fetcher -> Fetcher: Normalize to StationRainData
    note right: Convert raw measurements\ninto intensity (mm/h)
end
deactivate Fetcher

Fetcher --> RDM: List<StationRainData>
deactivate Fetcher

note right of RDM
  Aggregates data from
  multiple fetchers (if any)
end note

RDM --> RG: Unified List<StationRainData>
deactivate RDM

== 3. Simulation Loop Usage ==

RG -> RG: Filter by specific time frame\n& convert to RainDataPoint
note left of RG: Active points ready\nfor Kriging interpolation
deactivate RG
@enduml